These are Puzzles for 6x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-1::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: april, june
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: snowboarding, skiing
There are 2 different favourite colors: orange, fuchsia
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, bongani
2 different pets are kept: ferret, goat
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, collecting
1. the owner of the goat is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far right##1
4. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Birthday      | april       | june    |
| Sport           | skiing | snowboarding |
| Color   | fuchsia     | orange   |
| Cigar   | bongani  | bolivar     |
| Pet           | goat       | ferret     |
| Hobby     | board-games     | collecting        |

