.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: purple, light-blue
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cricket, basketball
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, crime
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, cain
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, october
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: orchid, bellflower
1. the cain-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
2. the person who likes light-blue is the cain-smoker##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
4. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |
| Color      | purple        | light-blue   |
| Sport         | basketball | cricket |
| Movie-Genre   | action     | crime   |
| Cigar   | aristoff       | cain     |
| Birthday           | october        | march    |
| Flower     | orchid  | bellflower    |

