.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-3::.
House: modern, craftsman
The people have 2 different hobbies: baking, writing
The people have 2 different jobs:  mechanic, dancer
There are 2 different favourite colors: lilac, black
2 different games are played: bridge, go
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, hot-chocolate
1. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
2. the mechanic is on the right of the craftsman house##1
3. the person who likes black is on the left of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |
| House          | craftsman    | modern      |
| Hobby         | writing   | baking       |
| Job   | dancer | mechanic |
| Color   | black  | lilac    |
| Game           | bridge       | go   |
| Beverage         | hot-chocolate   | milk     |

