.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-20::.
2 different games are played: backgammon, poker
There are 2 different favourite colors: blue, yellow
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: sports, spy
The people have 2 different hobbies: skydiving, singing
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: may, january
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, scooter
1. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
2. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
3. the person playing poker is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
4. the person watching sports movies is the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |
| Game      | backgammon    | poker      |
| Color          | blue | yellow |
| Movie-Genre           | spy     | sports      |
| Hobby   | singing    | skydiving       |
| Birthday           | january     | may      |
| Transport     | scooter   | bus         |

 